Ujunwa Eucharia Okafor (amụrụ 20 Disemba 1992) bụ onye egwuregwu bọọlụ Naịjirịa na -esonye n'egwu dịka onye mgbachitere
Ọ gbaara ALG Spor na Turkish Women's First Football League ma yiri nọmba jesi ederede iri anọ na anọ
N'afọ 2018, a kpọrọ ya ka ọ banye n'òtù mba ụmụ nwanyị Naijiria.
Okafor gbara egwuregwu bọọlụ na obodo ya na Nigeria Women Premier League bụ Delta Queens FC,   tupu ọ kwaga Turkey, wee sonye  nso nso a na otu ndị inyom mbụ kwalitere ọgbakọ ALG Spor na Gaziantep
N'ọnwa Febụwarị afọ 2018, a kpọrọ Okafor ka ọ bịa na otu mba ụmụ nwanyị Naịjirịa maka isonye na asọmpi Iko Mbaụwa 2018 WAFU
